{"type": "article", "id": 25199, "title": "澳大利亚皇家海军博物馆，一幢波浪一般的建筑物", "description": "它有连接潜艇和陆地以及展示的功能，看起来非常酷。", "date": "2016-04-11T07:08:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 20170, "name": "悉尼"}, {"id": 616, "name": "博物馆"}, {"id": 17732, "name": "海军"}, {"id": 26025, "name": "FJMT"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154448wP2x0NiAYhjmBHFd.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>澳大利亚国家海事博物馆（Australian National Maritime Museum，简称 ANMM）位于悉尼达令港(Darling Harbour)北端，最早开放于 1991 年，是澳大利亚政府直接管理的 6 个博物馆之一，也是当地重要的旅游景点。博物馆最令人兴奋的地方是港口停靠了 HMAS 吸血鬼号、HMAS 昂斯洛号和 HMAS 前进号这三艘退役的潜艇以供参观，其中吸血鬼号是澳大利亚皇家海军最后一艘大型枪船。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021544332YfqTOPLsyaiNGg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>海滨展馆（Waterside Pavilion）是 2015 年 11 月开放的新馆，它的位置原本是 HMAS 吸血鬼号和 HMAS 昂斯洛号之间的甲板。博物馆想要修建一个从甲板到达两艘潜艇的过渡的建筑，同时纪念第一次世界大战和服役 100 年的澳大利亚皇家海军。他们邀请澳大利亚的建筑事务所 FJMT 参与修建。</p>\n<p class=\"\">FJMT 沿着狭长形的位置修建了这个博物馆，占地大概 500 平方米。建筑表面是同样宽度铝制材料，每一块之间都有些微角度的相错，构成了略有起伏的波浪形状，它可以配合自然光产生波光的感觉。这个波浪到了建筑侧面的中心构成最大面积的开口，开口处安装了条形玻璃让这里显得通透。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">展馆的形状并不是很夸张，黑色本身是较为低调的，既满足了有自己的特征也能凸显出旁边潜艇的重要性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154434by5RZ2nVGIrcH4SC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154434IkFO5eEdVDBaiA7W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154435iKhbULdPuVnIxS65.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154436qbp7XlFu25swra1z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154437qcQOAmkwlPyr9H0a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154438uGSMfU7mRzDYO6oC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154438GZ98pri4RBDfOHlM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154439pHkuhRMmiJ3cQCIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021544401GrC4QpXy8WeFhko.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154440gi1H8t9qhLuR63FG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154441eKEoSNpr6FLAgwDk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">展馆本身充当了连接的功能。<br></figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154441NAcQhCSmbe7pBTld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154442lmZ5TkHgEXLfWUqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">狭长形的室内本身也有些像潜艇的内部构造，建筑师通过悬浮的风扇、鱼雷等物品营造了一种工业感。这里展示了海员生活的资料，包括日记、家书、照片等物品，让人体会到海军的生活。</p>\n<p class=\"\">海滨展馆成人票价 30 美元，<a href=\"http://www.actionstations.sydney/cn\">这里有相关参考信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154442ntGdxM5iAJEbUrBR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154443JjgyxvTQ1mZAoLfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154444VolgfaQIKUWukt7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021544449mPIl2i7Us4BnGFL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.69491525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154445HEtFAxp84dSP71sf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00200401\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154446s8P9IoyctOEmGkJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">HMAS 前进号</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154446FZv21ib7ErHJBqUk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">HMAS 昂斯洛号</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154447hLlkj52J8G7mb3od.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">HMAS 吸血鬼号</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154448jxatZD2XSLAhVIwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">“海床之墓”的雕塑</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/784955/the-waterfront-pavilion-australian-national-maritime-museum-fjmt-studio\"> archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.actionstations.sydney/cn\">actionstations</a></p>\n\n"}